        {
            "title": "未來10年值得持有的最佳科技股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ARXDoYMr3lNw2OJxNOPN1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/a53c765abcf2a54cce853350e7dbafb1\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場焦點被少數大型科技股壟斷之際，仍有其他科技公司同樣值得投資者留意，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Broadcom;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Broadcom\">Broadcom</a>（AVGO）便是當中之一。這家公司由傳統網絡及軟件企業，蛻變為與全球頂級雲端巨頭合作的尖端AI客製晶片供應商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Broadcom與同業的最大分別，在於其極強的財務實力；公司目前自由現金流約74億美元，既能持續派息，亦有充足資金支持未來增長，而最新業績進一步鞏固「Broadcom是業績火車頭」的市場印象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在2025年第四季度，Broadcom收入按年增長28%，自由現金流則按年上升36%；即使增長未來略為放緩，穩健的資產負債表仍為公司建立深厚護城河。公司亦在最近宣布把股息再提高10%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-59ab43b2-11fb-3e95-a009-18803f612bd3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Broadcom股價歷來波動不小，但耐心持有的投資者最終獲得豐厚回報；截至2月11日，該股12個月升幅約45%，過去5年累計更升615%，市值增加至逾1萬億美元，跻身全球市值最高企業之列。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更重要的是，Broadcom擁有極強執行力，現時手上高達1620億美元訂單，足以支撐公司未來10年的持續增長動能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作者：Catie Hogan, The Fool</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 HKMoneyClub</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多你或感興趣內容：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/14/%e9%87%8d%e6%ba%ab%e3%80%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%a3%87%e9%95%b7%e6%af%9b%e3%80%8ddavid-webb%e7%9a%848%e5%a4%a7%e9%95%b7%e7%b7%9a%e8%87%b4%e5%8b%9d%e6%b3%95%e5%89%87/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/28/%e7%99%bd%e9%8a%802025%e5%b9%b4%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%87144-%e4%bd%86%e6%ad%b7%e5%8f%b2%e6%9a%97%e7%a4%ba2026%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%96%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/30/%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83ai%e6%b3%a1%e6%b2%ab%e7%88%86%e7%a0%b4%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%993%e7%a8%ae%e8%bc%83%e7%a9%a9%e9%99%a3%e7%9a%84%e9%81%b8%e6%93%87%e5%8f%af%e7%82%ba%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e7%b5%84%e5%90%88/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">睇完新聞，記得追蹤hkmoneyclub以下平台，接收更多分析評論！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">YouTube：hkmoneyclub (https://www.youtube.com/@hkmoneyclub)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本文所提供的信息僅供一般參考之用，並不構成任何個人化的投資勸誘或建議。作者沒持有以上提及的股票。 HK MoneyClub (www.hkmoneyclub.com)</p></div>",
